<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink91-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">kuṟai vēṇṭip piṉṉiṉṟu vanta talaimakaṟkut tōḻi, ‘ivaḷ iḷaiyaḷ viḷaivilaḷ’ eṉac cēṭpaṭuttatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink91">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>neṟimarup perumai nīla virumpōttu</l>
<l>veṟimalarp poykai yāmpaṉ mayakkuṅ</l>
<l>kaḻaṉi yūraṉ makaḷivaḷ</l>
<l>paḻaṉa vetiriṉ koṭippiṇai yalaḷē.</l>
</lg>

<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>   She's the daughter (girlfriend?) of the man from the village with paddy fields</l> 
<l rend="indent4"> 	where a curling-horned, blue-black male buffalo </l> 
<l rend="indent4"> 	disturbs the white lotus in the pond with its perfumed blossoms – </l> 
<l> the girl with a garland of bamboo creepers from the tank.</l> 

</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
